name: Perssy
overview: Our website provides you with an effective and easy to use tool that will send you on a journey of self-discovery. Your strengths, weaknesses and everything in between will be highlighted; offering you the opportunity for self-improvement.The tool consists of two questionnaires that will gather an organic view of: who you are, what your personal beliefs are and your personality traits. The first questionnaire allows you to analyze yourself while the second one gives you the opportunity to view how others perceive you. Upon completion you will receive a comprehensive report that compares both results and provides constructive feedback that emphasizes areas for improvement.
